Package it.polimi.ingsw.messages.serverMessages

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ChangesDone
    Class ChangesDone is a Message used to communicate that a player has performed an action.
    CloseMessage
    Class CloseMessage represents a CustomMessage used by the server to communicate the end of the communication.
    CustomMessage
    Abstract class Custom message represents a generic Message that needs to be showed to the player.
    Disconnection
    Class Disconnection represents a CustomMessage used by the server used to communicate that a player has disconnected from the game or has reconnected to the game.
    ErrorMessage
    Class ErrorMessage represents an error CustomMessage that needs to be showed to the player.
    PlayersNumberMessage
    Class PlayersNumberMessage represents a CustomMessage used by the server used to inform the player of the available lobbies.
    SetupMessage
    Class SetupMessage represents a CustomMessage used by the server used to communicate things to the player before the game starts.
    TurnChange
    Class TurnChange is a Message used to communicate a turn change.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    ErrorType
    Enumeration ErrorType contains all the possible types of ErrorMessage.
